elsen til adressa.no.", "Han vil ikke uttale seg mer f\u00f8r de har mottatt rapporten fra sivilombudsmannen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "56bb6557b47bea7579c12a31541e2da63f27d2d2dad560b559ed030c4fcba39d"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-03-24T09:14:08.147Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I \u00e5rsmeldingen til sivilombudsmannen kommer det frem at sanit\u00e6rforholdene i Trondheim fengsel ikke holder akseptabel standard. Lang ventetid gj\u00f8r at fangene av og til m\u00e5 oppbevare avf\u00f8ringen i poser."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article8750177.ece/1fzjjy/BINARY/w980/IMG_fengsel_3-030113.jpg_2_1_395MJ21.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/674f2e3ef882c316dea1e47c4ffffde913d97e05.jpg?5830e3e6"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["\u2013 D\u00e5rlige sanit\u00e6rforhold i Trondheim fengsel -adressa.no", "Bruker doposer", "Gammelt problem"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "674f2e3ef882c316dea1e47c4ffffde913d97e05"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["trondheim fengsel", "oppbevart avf\u00f8ring", "toalett", "trondheim", "innsatte", "sivilombudsmann", "poser"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "trondheim og drammen"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["aage thor falkanger", "egil gabrielsen"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]